    <h2>Training</h2>
    <ol style="font-size:20px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
        <li style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 8px;">Exercise prescription is based on your personality, body type and current lifestyle.</li>
        <li style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 16px;">You will feel better, move better and become leaner.</li>
