<div style="padding-bottom: 1em;" class="contentSection YourExperience">
    <div class="CenterAndRestrictWidth">
        <h2 style="text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">Your Experience</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 no-gutters">
                <p style="padding-left: 36px; padding-right: 36px;">Your weights at the gym begin to increase drastically and you no longer have those painful niggles in your shoulders and back. Your friends are left wondering where you get your motivation from as when you cycle home from work you feel as if you have a new pair of legs. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 no-gutters">
                <p style="padding-left: 36px; padding-right: 36px;">We have been through this process with countless clients. It’s simply a case of small but specific changes having a profound positive effect. We want to empower you so that you understand why your back hurts, why running is/is not right for your body type and how to fix it.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


